data.description: View website: http://4765moorefieldmemorialhighway.AgentMarketing.com - Great buy on a bright and cheerful remodeled bungalow just outside of Pickens. Conveniently located, close to everything ,and is in move-in condition.  Featuring hardwood floors, tiled countertops, natural gas heat, and a fenced in yard. New roof installed in 2009, along with windows, and plumbing. Also has a 2 car carport, plus 2 workshops, one 12x14 and another 12x10 . Lots of options with this home, It was a daycare in the past, and is still zoned Commercial and Residential. You could use it as a home or a business.
